---
title: Events at Cathcart United Free Church
description: Upcoming events at Cathcart United Free Church, Glasgow.
activeNav: events
layout: base.njk
---

<div class="container">

    <h2>Events</h2>
    <p>Here you will find details of special events and activities coming up at Cathcart United Free Church
    and in our wider community. For our regular weekly meetings please see the
    <a href="/meetings/">Meetings page</a>.</p>

    {% set currentEventsList = collections.events | currentEvents %}
{% if currentEventsList and currentEventsList.length > 0 %}

{% set currentMonth = "" %}
{% for event in currentEventsList %}

    {% set eventMonth = event.date | dateMonthYear %}
    {% if eventMonth != currentMonth %}
        {% if not loop.first %}</div>{% endif %}
        <h3 class="event-month">{{ eventMonth }}</h3>
        <div class="event-list">
        {% set currentMonth = eventMonth %}
    {% endif %}

    <div class="event-card">
        {% if event.image %}
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="{{ event.image }}" 
                 alt="{{ event.imageAlt }}" 
                 class="news-image-{{ event.imageSize or 'medium' }}" />
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <p class="event-meta">
        {% if event.endDate %}
        {{ event.date | dateFormat }} – {{ event.endDate | dateFormat }}
        {% else %}
        {{ event.date | dateFormat }}
        {% endif %}
        {% if event.startTime %}
        &bull; {{ event.startTime }}{% if event.endTime %}–{{ event.endTime }}{% endif %}
        {% endif %}
        {% if event.location %} &bull; {{ event.location }}{% endif %}
        </p>
        <h3>{{ event.title }}</h3>
        {% if event.description %}
        <p>{{ event.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if event.details %}
        {{ event.details | markdown | safe }}
        {% endif %}
        {% if event.link %}
            {% if "http" in event.link %}
                <a href="{{ event.link }}" class="section-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ event.linkText or "Find out more" }} →</a>
            {% else %}
                <a href="{{ event.link }}" class="section-link">{{ event.linkText or "Find out more" }} →</a>
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
    </div>

{% endfor %}
</div>

{% else %}
<p>There are no upcoming events at the moment. Please check back soon.</p>
{% endif %}

    <!-- REGULAR EVENTS NOTE -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <div class="section-card-header">
            <h3>Regular Activities</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="section-card-body">
            <p>As well as the special events listed above, we have a number of regular activities
            running throughout the year. Please see the following pages for details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/meetings/">Sunday and Wednesday services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/prayer/#prayer-time">Monday prayer meetings</a></li>
                <li><a href="/church-life/">Fellowship groups, Moments Cafe, Quiet Spaces and Renew Wellbeing</a></li>
                <li><a href="/church-life/off-the-cuf/">Off the CUF — first Saturday of every month</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>